survey_response.review_text:
I went for wishdom tooth extraction treatment and dr. Biradar consulted me very nicely by explaining every minor things and dr umashankar operated it. I was so convinced that in two days only, I completed consultation + diagnosis + operation and third day i am perfectly all right. Thanks for such smooth experience. Couple of feedbacks for clinic, tough, I would like to give:
1) bp and sugar report requirement was told me later point of time, it would be always great that patient should know during initial consultation, so that he can feel more comfortable collecting all diagnostic reports at one shot.

2) do's and don't explained me after extraction, here, it would be really nice that patients should be informed twice about it - once before extraction and later just quick recap. It will set their mind very well and if any preparation like ice cube etc can be taken care comfortable way. Also, aftrr extraction patient wont be able to talk for sometime, sl creates communication gap for such details. 

3) power management could be slightly better, lots of trip can scare patients and their relatives.

I hope these feedback will help Impression team to do more greater thing as I found their mindset assertive. Thanks

Dr.Prafulla provided an excellent explanation of the procedure- thus expelling any fears/doubts related to the complex surgery. She was accommodative of my schedule & conducted the surgery keeping my personal time constraints in mind. The surgery was completely painless and she conducted the same seamlessly. I was very comfortable on the chair & was in-fact enjoying the background music being played in the clinic. On a jocular note- I also requested a change in the background music which was also complied with. She thoroughly explained the important after surgery care to be taken by me at home. She was also available to me on WhatsApp and asked me to contact her anytime- in case of questions or an emergency. I contacted her regarding a question and got an immediate response from her. All in all- a very satisfying experience & I would recommend her excellent treatment/care to anybody requiring the same.

Dr Prafulla is one of the most competent and understanding individuals that I’ve met till date. Not only does she understand the patients worry and apprehensions but she takes time in explaining and addressing every minute detail of the concern that one may have. I went to her with periodontitis and she administered a lazer flap gum surgery to relieve me of my problem. Her surgical capabilities surpass the ordinary. So smooth was the entire process ( though it’s a long procedure) that I didn’t even feel a thing and and am now on my way to healing and recovery.
I must also thank her entire team for being super efficient at fixing appointments as per my convenience and comfort. I would recommend this clinic hands down.

Dental problems were worrying me for a long time..but once i met doctor prafulla , felt better. She explained the problems I'm facing thoroughly n made me understand the importance of treatments to be undertaken. So I'm at ease now n looking forward to treatments that i shall undergo 😊👍

Madam thanks for the treatment except for some pain which is still there no serious problem. One thing the surgeon after reviewing my file asked me whether left side or right side. Whether upper portion or lower. If it was for confirmation ok but the way he asked was difficult to understand. No problem. 2nd thing the fees charged is really on very much higher side. I had expected it to be between Rs 2000_3000. Think of it. With regards Sreedhara R J

His talking style to the children is good. Nicely talk to the child try to do the treatment . First day my child was crying after second day she was not crying and he add lots of patience. Now she comfortable with the doctor and she friendly with the doctor .

Dr. Biradar is an exceptionally professional Doctor. My procedure was completed in a few sittings due to my unavailability. However each appointment was a delight! Starting from booking the appointment to the actual procedure. The results of the procedure is fantastic and I certainly reccomend Dr. Biradar!
